anpää</a> (1939)</span>&#160;<span class="sep-liste">·</span> <span class="nowrap"><small><i>non décerné</i></small> (1940–1943)</span>&#160;<span class="sep-liste">·</span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Johannes_V._Jensen" title="Johannes V. Jensen">Jensen</a> (1944)</span>&#160;<span class="sep-liste">·</span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Gabriela_Mistral" title="Gabriela Mistral">G. Mistral</a> (1945)</span>&#160;<span class="sep-liste">·</span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Hermann_Hesse" title="Hermann Hesse">Hesse</a> (1946)</span>&#160;<span class="sep-liste">·</span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Andr%C3%A9_Gide" title="André Gide">Gide</a> (1947)</span>&#160;<span class="sep-liste">·</span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/T._S._Eliot" title="T. S. Eliot">Eliot</a> (1948)</span>&#160;<span class="sep-liste">·</span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/William_Faulkner" title="William Faulkner">Faulkner</a> (1949)</span>&#160;<span class="sep-liste">·</span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Bertrand_Russell" title="Bertrand Russell">Russell</a> (1950)</span></td>
